author: robbie
msg: QPID-4809: change initial-config.json to using qpid.work_dir and qpid.home_dir config variables instead of QPID_WORK and QPID_HOME system properties
Enables us to default the former when QPID_WORK is not set and allows the latter to be set on a per-instance basis.
